--Project--
  [Domain Analysis]
    a registration layout that requires user to provide specific information in order to successfully register
  [Data Required]
    1. name
    2. email
    3. password
    4. re-enter password
    5. gender
    6. country
    7. agree checkbox
    8. pick image
  [Representation]
    a single interface that allows for input of all data. Need teviews for name email and password. Imageview for profile picture. Buttons (radio, checkbox, dropdown) for
    selecting gender (radio), country (dropdown), agree to terms (checkbox), register (simple button)
   
